Electabuzz (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0124: Jynx
Pokémon
#0126: Magmar →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Electabuzz (TCG Pocket).

Electabuzz has been featured on 32 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Electabuzz cards are normally Lightning-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Electabuzz

Electabuzz
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
